    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "growing and evolving doesn't really feel like it. it feels more like... decay. i'm not evolving, i'm just getting closer to the end, but i'm still stuck here. if the person i was meant to be is gone, then what's the point of keeping this version of me going? it just feels heavy and empty.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
