      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... it doesn't feel like \"finding a new direction.\" it feels like I'm just carrying around a corpse. i'm tired of pretending there's something alive in here. if the real me is gone, isn't there some kind of peace in just... letting the rest of it go?",
